Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,==========================================Main Text Strat==========================================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.85,0:01:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突入的话就无后路可退了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.07,0:01:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.36,0:01:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.32,0:01:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以确认的是 现在不得不去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.68,0:01:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.35,0:01:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了就会自己找出答案了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.25,0:02:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为“Flamehaze”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.84,0:02:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.05,0:02:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突入
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.25,0:02:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜 她保护了我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.89,0:02:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护了只不过是个“Mystes”的我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.70,0:02:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.96,0:02:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二 我要把悠二……
